A cool data analysis link

There are a lot of cool data analysis projects out there by now. Here is one from 538, which gives a nice interactive illustration of the phenomenon of p-hacking, which basically means investigators playing with data until they get something statistically significant - a problem that is very widespread in science. Well likely touch on that topic at some point in the course.
